# Agent runtime artifacts (generated, not source).
# Structured data lives in Postgres (STORAGE_ARCHITECTURE.md); the only
# on-disk runtime outputs are rendered markdown (reporting.py), harness
# reports, and the raw API response cache. The pre-Postgres file-based
# design's markets/ and flagged/ trees no longer exist.
rankings/*.json
rankings/*.md
snapshots/*.md
harness_reports/*.json
harness_reports/markets_dashboard.md
sources/*/
results.tsv            # Karpathy's original log name — same never-commit rule
experiment_log.tsv     # Karpathy AutoResearch experiment log — never commit

# CoStar exports (not committed - contains licensed data)
costar_exports/
*.xlsx
*.csv
# Phase 6 test fixtures are synthetic, not licensed CoStar data — commit them.
!tests/fixtures/costar/*.csv

# Database backups
*.sql
*.dump
backups/

# Playwright browser binaries
playwright/.local-browsers/

# Phase 10 runtime sentinels — local to a checkout, never committed.
.halt
.experiment_loop.lock
